{"tid":1865695,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"打尖搶籌 長者推撞跌倒","createTime":"2020-02-06T10:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T12:28:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4f83f2f7c8f09f41abfc19acf015aa1af454ab94","tid":1865695,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200206/SHQOV65WPXZSD4CJYSVHXZ7E4Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200206%2FSHQOV65WPXZSD4CJYSVHXZ7E4Y%2F&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsvuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=b1a72a51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200206%2FSHQOV65WPXZSD4CJYSVHXZ7E4Y%2F&h=bce48870\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200206/SHQOV65WPXZSD4CJYSVHXZ7E4Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n打尖搶籌 長者推撞跌倒<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】全城搶罩下，市面不少口罩遭炒至數百元一盒，令基層及長者難以負擔，甚至要循環再用。有團體昨早於觀塘免費向長者派發十萬個口罩，吸引逾千名長者清晨到場排隊，其間有人打尖，互相推撞，情況一度混亂。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：三方施壓奏效 林鄭終跪低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200206/large/1580923753_0d46.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200206%2Flarge%2F1580923753_0d46.gif&h=fcc37b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清晨時分，已有數百名長者到場排隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n婆婆口罩「年初四用到𠵱家」<br />\n<br />\n昨凌晨時分，翠屏道觀塘遊樂場硬地足球場已放置多個雪糕筒，並連上膠帶為派籌作準備。居於觀塘的陳婆婆，前晚11時許已到場排隊，她狠批政府不顧市民生死，「𠵱家我哋唔係叫你施捨，畀錢買都買唔到嗰度先死嘛！」活動原定由昨早10時，於觀塘翠屏道觀塘遊樂場開始，由於輪候長者已達千人，工作人員提早於8時派籌，領籌者需年滿65歲並親自領取，須出示長者卡或身份證，其間有人排完再排，並出現打尖情況，多人互有推撞，有長者跌倒，現場人士鼓譟，即使3,400個籌號已派完，大會宣佈截龍，惟球場外大批長者一擁而上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200206/large/1580923752_99b8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200206%2Flarge%2F1580923752_99b8.gif&h=0230bba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅婆婆<br />\n<br />\n由於天雨關係，主辦方香港愛馬女士協會提早派發口罩，每籌可獲發15個口罩，如有剩餘，口罩將全數送予弱勢社群、有特殊需要或緊急情況人士或服務此等人士的志願機構。成功取得口罩的79歲羅婆婆，獨居於翠屏邨，身上的口罩由年初四開始使用，「屋企一個都冇，晚晚洗完再戴。」家住將軍澳的80歲朱伯不滿指，「又話80歲以上可以打去留，電話都冇人聽，安排得唔好」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者簡明恩"},{"pid":"d651396be56be5609f42b790c60240f816dd28d9","tid":1865695,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45113be35d59d6b3c9f38a3036337d8cea63e44","tid":1865695,"uid":122275,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:27:22.000Z","msg":"其實重複戴仲易有菌 分分鐘衰過唔戴"},{"pid":"278a7dae51ea20f0d0268717839ae1f1759628aa","tid":1865695,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"咁好精力邊忽似有需要？"},{"pid":"40cf98b0e1595e0d2e2121701ef2ee8c8b91ac79","tid":1865695,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"又鬥慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744805df124841d192511d333350125173feb4aa","tid":1865695,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"問 呢班廢老係19841997至呢二十年來為抵擋支共入侵付出過咩"},{"pid":"a5a677d02e0f279707da4112b28f705a8899be82","tid":1865695,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:50:28.000Z","msg":"80歲以上級別MMA"},{"pid":"826d8b166ad50c62a4c6b8aac35f42c806cc9963","tid":1865695,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"觀塘真係多廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd398c0a976341954b6666ed5c5029eef0ff06d8","tid":1865695,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:28:12.000Z","msg":"唉,  呢個仆街